reviewText:
John Wayne's Video Library Volume One VHS 1934-35

B&W Black And White
Trans Global Video, Inc.
Printed in the U.S.A.
VHS video tape that plays on a vcr
UPC 098492008017

3 full length John Wayne Movies On One Video Tape
Features on this tape:
1. Blue Steel [1934]- Typical John Wayne excitement as he
rides into danger and violence.
2. Desert Trail [1935]- John Wayne stars as a rough and tough
cowboy in this western adventure.
3. Lawless Range [1935] - John Wayne and the posse save the
ranchers from trouble.
